import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter,Routes,Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Options from './components/Options'

function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path=''/>
        <Route path='/option' element={<Options/>}/>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
